OL,3,CFarmers say wet weather is having
OL,4,Cdeadly impact on lambing season
OL,6,FWith one of the wettest winters on
OL,7,Frecord in Wales, March and April have
OL,8,Fso far seen little let up, leaving
OL,9,Ffarmers unable to plant crops and put
OL,10,Flivestock outside.
OL,12,FWith agriculture emitting millions of
OL,13,Ftonnes of greenhouse gases every year,
OL,14,Fit's a sharp reminder of the role the
OL,15,Findustry plays in tackling climate
OL,16,Fchange.
OL,18,FIn Pendolyan in the Vale of Glamorgan,
OL,19,Ffarmer Tom Rees has been up to his
OL,20,Fankles in water.
