OL,4,Cdeadly impact on lambing season
OL,6,FThis time of year he should be sowing
OL,7,Fspring barley in this field, but that
OL,8,Fwindow has passed. Instead he'll have
OL,9,Fto plant maize, but it's still a
OL,10,Fmystery when, "(There's) no sign of it
OL,11,Fdrying up.
OL,13,F"It won't go in for at least another
OL,14,Fmonth or six weeks at this rate. It's
OL,15,Fgoing to take a long time to dry
OL,16,Fbefore we can get on the ground and
OL,17,Fspread muck, and then plough it.
