OL,3,CFarmers say wet weather is having
OL,4,Cdeadly impact on lambing season
OL,6,F"I just despair to know when we will
OL,7,Fget it in. Since last July we've had
OL,8,Fnon-stop rain. It's the worst farming
OL,9,Fyear that I've ever known since I've
OL,10,Fbeen home from college.
OL,12,F"And I've been home 15 years. It's
OL,13,Frain on rain on rain."
OL,15,FDespite the soggy weather, calving has
OL,16,Fbeen taking place but this year Tom is
OL,17,Fhaving to do it in the barn for the
OL,18,Ffirst time where it's dry.
OL,20,FIn Ynysybwl, Mathew Isaac has lost 30
OL,21,Flambs to the weather.
