OL,3,CFarmers say wet weather is having
OL,4,Cdeadly impact on lambing season
OL,6,FIt means some have developed joint
OL,7,Fproblems due to being exposed to the
OL,8,Fwet conditions.
OL,10,F"Anything that's a little bit weak,
OL,11,Fthey fall by the wayside," says Mathew.
OL,13,F"You're picking up dead lambs in the
OL,14,Fmorning then. We're at the limit of
OL,15,Fwhere we keep the sheep inside.
OL,17,F"When they're born they're only 24 or
OL,18,F48 hours old, and then they moved out.
OL,19,FThere's no way you could keep all the
OL,20,Fewes in with all the lambs.
