OL,6,F"The disease burden in here then would
OL,7,Fbe greater than what it is outside."
OL,9,FThe effects of climate change have
OL,10,Fbeen blamed for the increased
OL,11,Frainfall, making 2023 one of the
OL,12,Fwettest years since records began.
OL,14,FAbi Reader, from the NFU, told ITV
OL,15,Fthat farmers recognise the important
OL,16,Fpart they play in the fight against
OL,17,Fclimate change.
