OL,3,CFarmers say wet weather is having
OL,4,Cdeadly impact on lambing season
OL,6,FShe said, "We've got a commitment at
OL,7,FNFU Cymru for net zero by 2040. There
OL,8,Fare a number of steps we can put in
OL,9,Fplace to do that, but we can't do it
OL,10,Fon our own.
OL,12,FShe wants more help from the Welsh
OL,13,FGovernment in reaching solutions to
OL,14,Fthe climate crisis. "We're going to
OL,15,Fhave to have help because producing
OL,16,Ffood for the nation is a collective
OL,17,Fresponsibility.
