OL,3,CFarmers say wet weather is having
OL,4,Cdeadly impact on lambing season
OL,6,F"You need to make sure that this money
OL,7,Fcomes to help us deal with problems
OL,8,Flike this, because the weather is
OL,9,Fgoing to become more and more
OL,10,Fvolatile", Abi Reader said.
OL,12,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"Significant changes to our climate
OL,14,Fand weather will continue to develop
OL,15,Fover the next few decades, and it is
OL,16,Fessential that we take steps now to
OL,17,Fbuild resilience to the potential
OL,18,Fimpacts of climate change.
