OL,3,CFarmers say wet weather is having
OL,4,Cdeadly impact on lambing season
OL,6,F"In 2023 Wales experienced one of the
OL,7,Fwettest years on record and, in July
OL,8,Falone, we received close to 200% of
OL,9,Fthe long-term average rainfall.
OL,11,F"We are currently monitoring the
OL,12,Fimpact the wet weather may have on
OL,13,Ffarmers in Wales, including through
OL,14,Fthe UK wide Agriculture Market
OL,15,FMonitoring Group."
